00:36:30.981 --> 00:36:32.649 position:19.52%,start align:start size:53.81% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>That despicable tailor.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1165
00:36:32.649 --> 00:36:35.234 position:19.52%,start align:start size:69.05% line:84.62% 
